summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department, authorizing the improvement of Northeast 125th Street from a point approximately 400 feet east of 35th Avenue Northeast to Roosevelt Way Northeast, Roosevelt Way Northeast from Northeast 113th Street to Northeast 130th Street, and Fifth Avenue Northeast from Northeast 130th Street to Northeast 125th Street and the acquisition of right of way in connection therewith; making an appropriation from the Seattle General Arterial Improvement Bonds 1954 Fund, and a reimbursable appropriation from the Arterial City Street Fund therefor.
